Revision history for LucyX-Search-WildcardQuery

0.06 01 Sept 2014
 - pod fix(es)
 - pass boost through to child ORCompiler (required for Lucy 0.4.0)

0.05 4 Oct 2013
 - fix highlight_spans() to actually work

0.04 10 July 2013
 - turn off Stemming analyzer in tests, to clarify how wildcards work.
 - refactor internals to use delegate pattern with ORQuery and get rid of
   the WildcardScorer class

0.03 21 Oct 2011
 - fix to support 'subordinate' change in Lucy 0.2.2

0.02 23 Sept 2011
 - add highlighting spans support 

0.01 21 June 2011
 - Initial release. Forked from Search::Query::Dialect::Lucy.

